snippet.textDisplay: So... I think I know why the bath bombs weren't working in the press. Two of the bath bombs you used were Jelly Bombs and they aren't standard bath bomb ingredients. The typical jelly bomb only has pockets of the Jelly mixture that they add to a normal bath bomb mix in pre dried out disks, so the jelly mix gets released separately in the tub. So maybe because you blitzed the jelly mix in with everything it made it less structurely sound.
